Reebok Club C Cardi Dynamic Pink (W)
results.story: The Cardi B x Reebok women’s Club C ‘Dynamic Pink’ is suffused with the brash attitude of the Bronx rapper, highlighted by a vibrant monochromatic finish that unites the sneaker’s disparate elements. They include glossy patent leather paneling, see-through quarter panels and a soft textile heel tab. A sturdy pull loop emerges from the exposed foam tongue to deliver easy on and off. The low-top is mounted on a semi-translucent midsole, built with an exaggerated stack height and finished in the same candy-bright hue featured on the upper.

results.name: Wmns Air Max Excee 'Purple Pulse Multi'
Wmns React Escape Run 'Summit White Gold'
results.story: Specifically developed for female athletes, the Nike women’s React Escape Run ‘Summit White Gold’ utilizes a textile upper equipped with a wider padded collar, good for a comfortable fit around the ankle. Internal bands are integrated into the laces for midfoot lockdown, while semi-translucent side panels enhance the shoe’s breathability. A soft Nike React midsole is reinforced with a rubber outsole featuring a multi-directional traction pattern ideally suited for city running.

results.name: Nike Air Max 90 SE Black Safari (W)
Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Jungle Art'
Wmns Air Force 1 Shadow 'Stars'
results.story: The Nike women’s Air Force 1 Shadow ‘Stars’ offers a playfully reconstructed take on the iconic silhouette. The low-top features a white leather upper with a contrasting black eyestay and forefoot overlay, both rendered in tumbled black leather and stacked atop a contrast-hued second layer. The sneaker’s woven tongue tag, lateral side Swoosh and Nike branded heel tab are similarly doubled up. The latter features three silver stars, matching the reconfigured top eyelet. A slightly exaggerated midsole houses Nike Air cushioning in the heel for a smooth ride.

results.name: Nike Air Max 90 SE White Safari (W)
Wmns 574 'Varsity Gold'
results.story: The New Balance women’s 574 ‘Varsity Gold’ dresses the retro runner in a traditional blend of mesh and textured suede. An off-white leather ‘N’ decorates the quarter panel, matching the textile tongue and leather heel tab, while a burgundy molded heel counter provides a sharply contrasting pop of color. The sneaker is mounted on an ENCAP midsole, which combines lightweight EVA foam with a durable polyurethane rim. A gum rubber outsole delivers grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Twisted Hearts - Black'
results.story: Launching as part of the brand’s Valentine’s Day collection, the Converse women’s Twisted Hearts Chuck Taylor All Star ‘Black’ carries a canvas upper with an all-over print made up of ivory hearts. A lone purple foil accent heart delivers an unexpected burst of color, along with a pink All Star patch on the medial ankle. Lightweight cushioning is provided by an OrthoLite insole. The high-top rests on a white rubber midsole, supported underfoot by a diamond-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns 574 'Light Burgundy'
results.story: The New Balance women’s 574 ‘Light Burgundy’ combines cushioned comfort with vintage ‘80s running style. A rich maroon hue is applied to the mesh and suede upper, accented with a white leather ‘N’ logo on the quarter panel. A molded yellow heel counter gives way to a two-tone ENCAP midsole, featuring a plush core of lightweight EVA foam with a durable polyurethane rim. Underfoot, a durable gum rubber outsole provides optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns 574 2E Wide 'Varsity Gold'
results.story: The New Balance women’s 574 2E Wide ‘Varsity Gold’ treats the retro runner to a warm color palette attuned to its ‘80s roots. A mustard yellow hue floods the mesh and suede upper, contrasted by white leather detailing on the heel tab and signature ‘N’ logo. A burgundy molded heel counter gives way to a two-tone ENCAP midsole, which combines a plush EVA foam core with a durable polyurethane rim. A gum rubber outsole provides grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Love Fearlessly'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘Love Fearlessly’ celebrates Valentine’s Day with a black and white canvas upper with unique graphics. A red heart-shaped icon adorns the rubber toe cap, while a repeating ‘Love Yourself’ print is emblazoned on the sneaker’s lateral and medial sides, the latter further accented with translucent All Star ankle patch. Inscribed on the interior tongue is a message that suggests ‘Love Yourself First.’ A solid white midsole anchors the high-top silhouette.

results.name: Wmns ZigWild Trail 6 'Cool Shadow Seaport Teal'
results.story: The Reebok women’s ZigWild Trail 6 ‘Cool Shadow Seaport Teal’ spotlights the lifestyle runner’s unique tooling. A dark teal finish is applied to the ZigTech midsole, featuring an innovative zigzag configuration designed to disperse energy through each stride. A high-traction rubber outsole gives the nod to classic trail runners from the ‘90s. Up top, the grey textile build is secured with partially concealed ghillie style lacing. Tonal synthetic leather overlays and no-sew skins provide lightweight support and durability.

results.name: Wmns Future Rider 'Galentine's Day - White'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Future Rider Galentine’s Day ‘White’ showcases subdued, neutral tones in honor of the February 13 holiday that originated from the TV show ‘Park and Recreation’ as a celebration of female friendships. The upper is constructed from light grey textile with tonal suede overlays and a white leather quarter panel. PUMA’s jumping cat logo lands on a star-shaped lace jewel and patent leather heel tab, while discreet ‘GRL PWR’ tags adorn the lateral heel of the right and left shoe. A secondary heart-shaped lace jewel features a simple PUMA wordmark.

results.name: Wmns ZX 2K Boost 'Grey Crew Blue'
results.story: The adidas women’s ZX 2K Boost ‘Grey Crew Blue’ highlights subtle pops of color on an otherwise neutral rendition of the responsive lifestyle runner. An integrated lacing system secures the grey textile upper, accented with blue three-stripes, a yellow forefoot overlay, pink collar binding and a peach-colored heel tab. The streamlined build is supported by a full-length Boost midsole, partially enveloped in a matching grey TPU cage for added durability and support.

results.name: Wmns 574 2E Wide 'Captain Blue'
results.story: The New Balance women’s 574 2E Wide ‘Captain Blue’ combines all-day comfort with ‘80s running style. A vibrant royal blue finish is executed on the upper, composed of breathable mesh with tonal suede overlays. The signature ‘N’ logo is stitched onto the quarter panel in white leather, matching the New Balance branded heel tab. A contrasting pop of orange makes its way to the molded heel counter and ENCAP midsole, featuring soft EVA foam and a durable polyurethane rim.

results.name: Wmns 574 'Captain Blue'
results.story: The New Balance women’s 574 ‘Captain Blue’ applies a vibrant palette to the vintage running shoe originally released in 1988. The upper combines breathable blue mesh on the toe box and collar with tonal suede overlays. Contrasting white leather is utilized on the ‘N’ logo and heel tab, inscribed with a New Balance wordmark. A molded orange heel counter offers rearfoot stability, while an ENCAP midsole delivers lightweight cushioning. Underfoot, a gum rubber outsole provides reliable grip.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam 1080v11 'White Bleached Lime Glow'
results.story: The New Balance women’s Fresh Foam 1080v11 ‘White Bleached Lime Glow’ delivers an ultra-plush ride in a lightweight package. A neon green ‘N’ logo adorns the knit textile upper, crafted with strategic zones of stretch and support. A molded Ultra Heel hugs the back of the foot, while an Ortholite sockliner provides lightweight cushioning. The sock-like build is mounted on a stacked Fresh Foam midsole, featuring rocker-shape geometry for a smooth transition.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam 1080v11 2A Wide 'White Bleached Lime Glow'
results.story: The New Balance women’s Fresh Foam 1080v11 4E Wide ‘White Bleached Lime Glow’ highlights vibrant accents on a lightweight silhouette made for daily runs. They neutral white and grey tones of the textile knit upper are contrasted by New Balance branding on the tongue and an outlined ‘N’ on the quarter panel. A molded Ultra Heel cradles the back of the foot. Responsive cushioning is provided by a Fresh Foam midsole, featuring a rocker shape that enables a smooth transition from heel strike to toe off.

results.name: Wmns ZigWild Trail 6 'Grey Twisted Coral'
results.story: The Reebok women’s ZigWild Trail 6 ‘Grey Twisted Coral’ applies sharply contrasting colors to a lifestyle runner that blends modern tooling with a ‘90s outdoor aesthetic. Ghillie style lacing secures a grey textile upper with tonal synthetic overlays and no-sew skins in a Ceramic Pink finish. The same pastel hue is applied to the padded collar, which combines with a breathable mesh tongue to deliver a comfortable fit. Underfoot, Reebok’s ZigTech midsole is engineered to disperse energy with each step.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam 1080v11 2E Wide 'White Bleached Lime Glow'
results.story: The New Balance women’s Fresh Foam 1080v11 2E Wide ‘White Bleached Lime Glow’ showcases vivid accents on a bootie-style upper, constructed from airy knit textile that combines alternating zones of stretch and support. A seamless Ultra Heel design cradles the back of the foot and Achilles for a snug, comfortable fit. An 8mm drop distinguishes the rocker-shaped Fresh Foam midsole, featuring precision engineered cushioning supplemented by an Ortholite sockliner.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Low 'Digital Daze Double Upper - Leopard'
results.story: The Converse women’s Digital Daze Double Upper Chuck Taylor All Star ‘Leopard’ updates the iconic silhouette with a dual-layered canvas build. The sneaker’s black exterior is contrasted by a Hyper Pink interior layer covered in a digitized leopard print. Both are equipped with a full set of chrome eyelets, allowing for multiple lacing options and a custom look. The low-top is mounted on a white rubber midsole, accented with contrasting black pinstripes.

results.name: Wmns 574 2E Wide 'Light Burgundy'
results.story: The New Balance women’s 574 2E Wide ‘Light Burgundy’ updates the versatile lifestyle runner with a rich, autumnal color palette. The upper combines a burgundy mesh base with tonal suede overlays at the forefoot, heel and quarter panel, the latter embellished with a white leather ‘N.’ Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of New Balance’s ENCAP midsole, built with a soft EVA core and durable polyurethane rim. A gum rubber outsole delivers grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Low 'Love Fearlessly'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Low ‘Love Fearlessly’ gets ready for Valentine’s Day with a two-tone color scheme and unique all-over graphics. The ivory-colored canvas upper is plastered with crimson text that reads ‘Love Fearlessly,’ while a matching red heart adorns the white rubber toe cap. A translucent Converse All Star tag is stitched onto the tongue, the interior side of which features a reminder to ‘Love Yourself First.’ The low-top is mounted on a solid white rubber midsole, accented with a contrasting red toe bumper and vintage license plate.

results.name: Wmns ZigWild Trail 6 'Black Pink'
results.story: The Reebok women’s ZigWild Trail 6 ‘Black Pink’ adds vibrant accents to a stealthy colorway of the durable running shoe. Fuchsia branding elements enliven the black textile upper, reinforced with textured synthetic leather overlays and abrasion-resistant no-sew skins. The same hot pink hue is applied to the low-profile midsole, supported by a distinctive ZigTech outsole that efficiently disperses energy for a smooth transition from heel strike to toe-off.

results.name: Wmns Nano X1 'Black Cool Shadow'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Nano X1 ‘Black Cool Shadow’ presents a stealthy colorway of a performance training shoe built for versatile fitness activities. The streamlined silhouette utilizes a Flexweave knit upper, featuring a Comfort Collar for a locked-in fit and a refined toe shape for a wide range of movements. A molded Speed Chassis heel counter swoops down to the midsole, which combines impact absorbing EVA with responsive Floatride Energy Foam under the ball of the foot.

results.name: Wmns Nano X1 'White Gum'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Nano X1 ‘White Gum’ updates the versatile training shoe with a pristine palette that accentuates its airy build. Flexweave knit is utilized on the upper, featuring a streamlined shape suitable for running. Reebok’s Comfort Collar delivers a locked-in fit, while the Speed Chassis heel counter offers rearfoot stability. The midsole combines soft EVA foam with energy-returning Floatride Energy Foam in the forefoot, which is supported by a gum rubber outsole for optimal grip.

results.name: Les Mills x Wmns Nano X1 'White Vector Navy'
results.story: The Les Mills x Reebok women’s Nano X1 ‘White Vector Navy’ highlights the shoe’s performance capabilities through a partnership with the international training program. Those benefits include a breathable Flexweave upper in a clean white finish, along with a contrasting black Speed Chassis that delivers added stability during quick movements. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of an EVA midsole, featuring a responsive forefoot insert made of Floatride Energy Foam.

results.name: Wmns Cali Star 'White Black'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Cali Star ‘White Black’ delivers a modern take on the vintage California silhouette, highlighted by an exaggerated rubber midsole. Up top, crisp white leather upper is reinforced with tonal suede overlays at the eyestay and heel. A contrasting black PUMA Formstrip decorates each of the sneaker’s side panels. Perforated detailing at the midfoot and toe box offers improved breathability, while a polyurethane sockliner provides lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Wmns Nano X1 Grit 'Grey Orange Flare'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Nano X1 Grit ‘Grey Orange Flare’ delivers a versatile training shoe made for a wide range of fitness activities, including HIIT, bootcamp and boxing. This Flexweave Grit variation makes use of an extra-durable woven textile upper, rendered in a neutral grey finish and featuring strategic areas of stretch and support in key performance areas. Contrasting orange accents land on the heel and EVA midsole, enhanced with Floatride Energy Foam cushioning typically utilized on the brand’s running shoes.

results.name: Wmns Mirage Mox 'Steel Grey Eggnog'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Mirage Mox ‘Steel Grey Eggnog’ updates the lifestyle runner with a color palette that mixes subdued earth tones with vibrant pops of color. Light grey mesh is utilized on the upper, fortified with leather, suede and nubuck overlays in varying shades of grey and brown. Fuchsia detailing stands out on the midfoot and heel, while bright aqua accents land on the textile collar lining and molded TPU heel counter. Those same hues enliven the off-white EVA midsole.

results.name: Wmns Nano X1 'Black Orange Flare'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Nano X1 ‘Black Orange Flare’ updates the performance training shoe with sharply contrasting hues. Black Flexweave is utilized on the upper, featuring knitted construction characterized by its superior breathability. A contrasting coral hue makes its way to the Speed Chassis heel counter, which extends to the EVA midsole. Floatride Energy Foam is added to the forefoot for energy return with each step. A two-tone rubber outsole in neon yellow and Radiant Aqua provides grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: Wmns Nano X1 'Digital Glow'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Nano X1 ‘Digital Glow’ showcases a vivid color palette on a versatile training shoe engineered to meet the varied demands of modern fitness enthusiasts. Lightweight and breathable Flexweave is utilized on the upper, rendered in a streamlined shape suitable for running. The Speed Chassis heel counter combines with an updated last to provide a stable platform for weighted exercises. The sneaker is mounted on a plush EVA midsole with responsive Floatride Energy Foam in the forefoot.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Lugged High 'Alt Exploration - Light Carbon'
results.story: The Converse women’s Alt Exploration Lugged Chuck Taylor All Star ‘Light Carbon’ updates the vintage high-top with a peached twill upper, lined in recycled mesh for breathable comfort. The sneaker rides on an elevated platform midsole, its solid white sidewalls matched by a rubber outsole with a traditional diamond traction pattern and exaggerated lugs. Standard branding elements include a Converse All Star license plate and a circular ankle patch on the medial side.

adidas NMD R1 HER Studios Floral (W)
results.story: The Her Studio London x adidas women’s NMD_R1 ‘Floral’ treats the lifestyle runner to a graphic-intensive makeover, courtesy of the textile print studio based in East London. The sneaker’s one-piece black textile upper is offset by a contrasting red pull tab and a multi-color floral print on the heel patch and signature three-stripes. The sock-like upper sits on a full-length Boost midsole, its lateral sidewall fitted with EVA plugs in contrasting teal and black hues.

Wmns Five Ten Freerider Primeblue 'Acid Mint Gum'
results.story: The adidas women’s Five Ten Freerider Primeblue ‘Acid Mint Gum’ treats the mountain biking shoe to a simplistic two-tone color scheme. A subdued teal finish is applied to a breathable textile upper made in part with Primeblue, featuring high-performance recycled materials that include Parley Ocean Plastic. The sneaker is mounted on a one-piece gum rubber cupsole, equipped with a distinctive Dotty tread keep designed to keep feet planted on the pedals.

results.name: Her Studio London x Wmns Sleek 'Floral'
results.story: The Her Studio London x adidas women’s Sleek ‘Floral’ updates the lifestyle silhouette with embroidered blossoms on the lateral side panel. The floral graphics, provided by the textile print studio based in East London, stand out against a dark navy leather backdrop. Soft pastel accents land on the heel tab and adidas logo window on the lateral eyestay. The low-top rests on a white rubber midsole, supported by an old-school herringbone traction outsole.

results.name: Wmns Superstar 'Heart Logo - White'
results.story: The adidas women’s Superstar ‘Heart Logo’ updates the iconic sneaker with luxe details and refreshed branding elements. The low-top makes use of a crisp white leather upper, accented with contrasting black velvet on the heel tab and signature three-stripes. They’re joined by an adidas Trefoil and an accompanying heart graphic embroidered on the lateral heel. The sneaker rides on a standard rubber cupsole, outfitted with a herringbone traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam Roav 'UV Glow Virtual Sky'
Wmns Nizza RF Platform 'Heart Embossed - Scarlet'
results.story: The adidas women’s Nizza RF Platform ‘Heart Embossed’ treats the reinvented retro hoops shoe to a simplistic two-tone color scheme. The scarlet leather upper is accented with contrasting white leather on the heel tab and signature three-stripes, the latter components enlivened with a tonal print made up of embossed hearts and Trefoils. The pattern is repeated on the sockliner, while the sneaker’s top eyelets are rendered in heart-shaped form. A towering platform midsole anchors the low-profile silhouette.

results.name: Wmns React Metcon Turbo 'White Metallic Gold'
Wmns Sleek 'Heart Embossed - White Scarlet'
results.story: The adidas women’s Sleek ‘Heart Embossed’ adds subtle romantic details to the minimalist silhouette, highlighted by white leather upper covered in a tonal all-over print made up of embossed hearts and adidas Trefoils. The sneaker’s top eyelets are shaped like hearts and painted red, matching the heel tab and adidas branding on the lateral logo window. Additional details include perforated three-stripes and a classic herringbone traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Air VaporMax 2020 Flyknit 'Violet Ash Volt'
Swarovski x Wmns Sambarose 'Cloud White'
results.story: An exclusive colorway made for Valentine’s Day, the Swarovski x adidas women’s Sambarose ‘Cloud White’ comes with a removable metallic gold charm encrusted with crystals. A subtle off-white finish is applied to the leather upper, modeled after the classic Samba and stamped with ‘Swarovski Crystals’ on the lateral heel in pink lettering. The same hue is repeated on zigzag stitching around the heel tab and an adidas Trefoil logo atop the tongue. A rubber platform midsole anchors the low-top.
